1
00:00:02,420 --> 00:00:05,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Stop!!</font>

2
00:00:19,520 --> 00:00:22,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What just happened?</font>

3
00:00:28,730 --> 00:00:30,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm so sorry, Big Brother...</font>

4
00:00:31,190 --> 00:00:32,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Because of me, you...</font>

5
00:00:32,570 --> 00:00:35,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's not your fault, Sarah.
Don't worry about it.</font>

6
00:00:35,610 --> 00:00:38,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">When I felt like,
I wanted to save you,</font>

7
00:00:38,530 --> 00:00:40,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">fire shot out of my body.</font>

8
00:00:41,500 --> 00:00:43,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Am I sick?</font>

9
00:00:43,960 --> 00:00:45,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're not sick, Sarah!</font>

10
00:00:46,670 --> 00:00:47,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Damn it...</font>

11
00:00:47,920 --> 00:00:50,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What is happening to her?</font>

12
00:00:52,550 --> 00:00:55,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's going to happen to me?</font>

13
00:00:56,840 --> 00:01:00,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm scared, Big Brother!
I'm so scared!</font>

14
00:01:02,890 --> 00:01:06,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No matter what happens,
I'll protect you.</font>

15
00:01:06,730 --> 00:01:08,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't worry, Sarah.</font>

16
00:01:12,280 --> 00:01:13,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Big Brother!</font>

17
00:01:13,490 --> 00:01:16,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Big Brother!</font>

18
00:01:16,450 --> 00:01:18,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">S-Sarah!</font>

19
00:01:18,620 --> 00:01:20,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Big Brother!</font>

20
00:01:21,790 --> 00:01:23,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sarah!</font>

21
00:01:23,540 --> 00:01:26,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Big Brother!</font>

22
00:01:33,130 --> 00:01:34,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Big Brother...</font>

23
00:01:35,470 --> 00:01:37,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">S-Sarah?</font>

24
00:01:40,100 --> 00:01:43,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why didn't you save me?</font>

25
00:01:43,350 --> 00:01:46,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You promised
you would protect me!</font>

26
00:01:59,200 --> 00:02:01,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Damn it...
That same dream again.</font>

27
00:03:48,970 --> 00:03:51,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}EPISODE 7
CROWING OVER A FEATHER</font>

28
00:04:10,000 --> 00:04:12,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I want to play in the sand too!</font>

29
00:04:15,250 --> 00:04:18,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Piyoko, Keiji's having a sand bath.</font>

30
00:04:18,130 --> 00:04:18,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

31
00:04:19,010 --> 00:04:23,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Chickens sand bathe to remove bugs
and impurities from our feathers.</font>

32
00:04:23,800 --> 00:04:27,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The same way humans bathe
to stay clean and healthy.</font>

33
00:04:27,720 --> 00:04:29,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh...</font>

34
00:04:29,180 --> 00:04:32,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">However, I opt for
a more sophisticated method.</font>

35
00:04:32,520 --> 00:04:35,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I use this!
Bug spray for female chickens!</font>

36
00:04:36,520 --> 00:04:40,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">An elegant woman must opt
for an elegant solution!</font>

37
00:04:40,610 --> 00:04:41,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh...</font>

38
00:04:44,780 --> 00:04:46,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Uh, excuse me...</font>

39
00:04:47,660 --> 00:04:49,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you the chickens
who fight against Demons?</font>

40
00:04:50,160 --> 00:04:51,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How do you know that?</font>

41
00:04:51,580 --> 00:04:52,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I knew it!</font>

42
00:04:52,660 --> 00:04:54,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Whoa! Awesome!</font>

43
00:04:54,500 --> 00:04:56,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We've seen you
on the human's phones.</font>

44
00:04:56,290 --> 00:04:58,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're even famous
in the pigeon world!</font>

45
00:04:58,710 --> 00:05:02,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We're seeing them in real lfe!
They're so cool!</font>

46
00:05:03,050 --> 00:05:04,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Um, If you say so...</font>

47
00:05:05,130 --> 00:05:06,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is kind of making me blush...</font>

48
00:05:07,090 --> 00:05:10,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh! Why don't we ask him?</font>

49
00:05:10,180 --> 00:05:12,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?
There's no way he'd accept!</font>

50
00:05:12,310 --> 00:05:13,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It seems like he's with his family.</font>

51
00:05:14,060 --> 00:05:15,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It won't hurt to ask...</font>

52
00:05:17,400 --> 00:05:20,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Uh, would you be interested...</font>

53
00:05:21,570 --> 00:05:23,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">...in joining us for a group date?</font>

54
00:05:23,110 --> 00:05:24,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A group date?</font>

55
00:05:24,570 --> 00:05:27,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You mean one of those
things human males and females do?</font>

56
00:05:27,620 --> 00:05:30,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes! They're very popular
in the pigeon world right now.</font>

57
00:05:30,740 --> 00:05:32,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">P-Popular?!</font>

58
00:05:32,540 --> 00:05:33,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I had no idea...</font>

59
00:05:33,830 --> 00:05:37,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Our third had to go on
a last-minute carrier pigeon job,</font>

60
00:05:37,750 --> 00:05:39,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">so he just canceled.</font>

61
00:05:39,250 --> 00:05:41,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So we were wondering
if you'd be interested</font>

62
00:05:41,130 --> 00:05:42,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">in joining us in his place?</font>

63
00:05:42,460 --> 00:05:43,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Me?</font>

64
00:05:43,510 --> 00:05:45,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Honestly, I 'm not interested in pigeons.</font>

65
00:05:46,090 --> 00:05:47,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please, just come with us!</font>

66
00:05:48,010 --> 00:05:51,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">With you there,
there will be so much to talk about!</font>

67
00:05:51,220 --> 00:05:53,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Plus, I think the ladies would
love to talk to a hero!</font>

68
00:05:53,890 --> 00:05:56,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please, just come for a little bit!</font>

69
00:05:57,520 --> 00:06:01,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sounds like fun.
Keiji, you should go with them.</font>

70
00:06:04,360 --> 00:06:07,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">W-Well, if you all insist...</font>

71
00:06:07,070 --> 00:06:08,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I guess I can go
for a little.</font>

72
00:06:08,700 --> 00:06:10,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">- Thank you very much!
- Thank you very much!</font>

73
00:06:16,120 --> 00:06:18,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?!
Why is there a chicken here?</font>

74
00:06:18,710 --> 00:06:21,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What a bummer.</font>

75
00:06:21,420 --> 00:06:23,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Looks like this meet-up's a dud.</font>

76
00:06:23,590 --> 00:06:26,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This isn't what you promised.</font>

77
00:06:26,420 --> 00:06:28,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">S-Sorry! Huh, that's weird!</font>

78
00:06:28,880 --> 00:06:29,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You don't recognize him?</font>

79
00:06:30,050 --> 00:06:32,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's the famous rooster
who fights monsters!</font>

80
00:06:33,010 --> 00:06:34,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">- Never heard of him.
- Never heard of him.</font>

81
00:06:35,270 --> 00:06:38,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Anyways, chickens can't fly.
That's not cool.</font>

82
00:06:38,890 --> 00:06:42,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They go "kokekokko"
and it's kind of weird.</font>

83
00:06:42,730 --> 00:06:45,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's that dangling from his chin?
Gross!</font>

84
00:06:45,900 --> 00:06:50,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What did you say?!</font>

85
00:06:50,780 --> 00:06:52,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey you!</font>

86
00:06:52,530 --> 00:06:54,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't tease the Mister!</font>

87
00:06:55,790 --> 00:06:57,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Piyoko, calm down.</font>

88
00:06:57,620 --> 00:06:58,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Keiji, listen up.</font>

89
00:06:59,460 --> 00:07:00,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">To be honest,</font>

90
00:07:00,460 --> 00:07:03,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't stand hearing them
slandering us like that.</font>

91
00:07:03,880 --> 00:07:05,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm steaming mad!</font>

92
00:07:06,010 --> 00:07:08,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It really makes my crown curl!</font>

93
00:07:08,510 --> 00:07:10,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But Keiji, no violence.</font>

94
00:07:11,140 --> 00:07:13,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is a group date.
The battlefield is a social one.</font>

95
00:07:14,260 --> 00:07:16,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So we need to woo them
on this date</font>

96
00:07:16,520 --> 00:07:18,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">by showing them
how awesome chickens truly are.</font>

97
00:07:19,060 --> 00:07:21,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's how we win.</font>

98
00:07:23,270 --> 00:07:26,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see.
So it all rests on my shoulders.</font>

99
00:07:27,320 --> 00:07:28,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Leave it to me.</font>

100
00:07:29,320 --> 00:07:32,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My pride as a chicken is
on the line in this battle...</font>

101
00:07:32,950 --> 00:07:34,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I mean date.</font>

102
00:07:35,790 --> 00:07:40,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll use my undeniable appeal and
make them fall in love with me!</font>

103
00:07:40,460 --> 00:07:41,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Uh...?</font>

104
00:07:41,290 --> 00:07:43,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Go get 'em, Mister!</font>

105
00:07:44,130 --> 00:07:47,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">- Something seems off.
- Go get 'em, Mister! Go get 'em!</font>

106
00:07:47,300 --> 00:07:49,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">- I hope he'll be all right.
- Go get 'em, Mister!</font>

107
00:07:50,170 --> 00:07:51,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's start with intros!</font>

108
00:07:52,090 --> 00:07:53,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm Ken!</font>

109
00:07:53,220 --> 00:07:54,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm Masa. Nice to meet you.</font>

110
00:07:57,520 --> 00:07:58,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm Ann.</font>

111
00:07:58,640 --> 00:07:59,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm Seiko.</font>

112
00:07:59,730 --> 00:08:01,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm Marin. Nice to meet you.</font>

113
00:08:03,520 --> 00:08:04,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My...</font>

114
00:08:04,900 --> 00:08:05,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Name is...</font>

115
00:08:14,530 --> 00:08:16,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ah! Keiji!</font>

116
00:08:17,160 --> 00:08:20,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You are so cool, Mister!</font>

117
00:08:20,500 --> 00:08:21,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not cool.</font>

118
00:08:22,000 --> 00:08:23,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Cringe.</font>

119
00:08:23,330 --> 00:08:24,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Gross.</font>

120
00:08:28,250 --> 00:08:29,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I should have seen this coming.</font>

121
00:08:32,340 --> 00:08:33,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wow!</font>

122
00:08:34,260 --> 00:08:36,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Amazing, you're a racing pigeon!</font>

123
00:08:36,970 --> 00:08:39,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We pigeons have
an instinctual sense of direction,</font>

124
00:08:39,100 --> 00:08:41,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">so I can fly out a 100 kilometers
and still find my way home.</font>

125
00:08:41,560 --> 00:08:44,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now's your chance to
show them what you've got!</font>

126
00:08:45,230 --> 00:08:46,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Uh, okay!</font>

127
00:08:46,480 --> 00:08:48,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Chickens are great too, you know!</font>

128
00:08:49,570 --> 00:08:51,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We get up early and our voices are loud.</font>

129
00:08:51,490 --> 00:08:53,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That is so annoying in the
morning!</font>

130
00:08:53,650 --> 00:08:54,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's so loud, huh?</font>

131
00:08:55,660 --> 00:08:57,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Something else! Something else!</font>

132
00:08:57,410 --> 00:08:58,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We run fast!</font>

133
00:08:58,530 --> 00:09:00,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Flying is faster...</font>

134
00:09:00,290 --> 00:09:01,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yup.</font>

135
00:09:01,160 --> 00:09:02,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Doesn't seem too efficient.</font>

136
00:09:02,750 --> 00:09:04,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">- I know!
- I know!</font>

137
00:09:05,790 --> 00:09:07,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We have big crowns!</font>

138
00:09:07,880 --> 00:09:10,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Crowns aren't really that necessary!</font>

139
00:09:12,170 --> 00:09:14,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We forget about bad things
in three seconds!</font>

140
00:09:14,590 --> 00:09:16,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't think it's just
about the bad things.</font>

141
00:09:17,600 --> 00:09:19,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ugh. He doesn't seem too smart.</font>

142
00:09:19,430 --> 00:09:20,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm a hard pass on a
lack of smarts.</font>

143
00:09:20,930 --> 00:09:22,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Agreed!</font>

144
00:09:22,100 --> 00:09:23,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is getting more
and more unbearable.</font>

145
00:09:23,850 --> 00:09:25,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I feel kind of bad for him.</font>

146
00:09:25,560 --> 00:09:28,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's enough!</font>

147
00:09:35,240 --> 00:09:38,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't care what
you think about chickens.</font>

148
00:09:38,870 --> 00:09:42,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">As long as I live a life with pride,
that's all that matters.</font>

149
00:09:44,750 --> 00:09:47,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll walk the path I choose.</font>

150
00:09:47,790 --> 00:09:49,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's all I can do.</font>

151
00:09:51,840 --> 00:09:54,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">- So cool!
- So cool!</font>

152
00:09:55,590 --> 00:09:58,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've never met such a manly bird!</font>

153
00:09:58,640 --> 00:10:01,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've been looking for a man
just like him!</font>

154
00:10:01,260 --> 00:10:03,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you look close,
he's actually hot.</font>

155
00:10:03,430 --> 00:10:04,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? What?</font>

156
00:10:05,640 --> 00:10:08,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I...don't really get it...
Is this what they call...</font>

157
00:10:10,730 --> 00:10:15,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A walk-off home run?!</font>

158
00:10:15,440 --> 00:10:16,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Will you go out with me?</font>

159
00:10:16,650 --> 00:10:17,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, me!</font>

160
00:10:17,530 --> 00:10:19,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Marry me!</font>

161
00:10:19,370 --> 00:10:21,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">- Hey! The Mister is my husband!
- Please!</font>

162
00:10:23,040 --> 00:10:25,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What is going on here?</font>

163
00:10:25,410 --> 00:10:27,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, ya got me here...</font>

164
00:10:28,040 --> 00:10:30,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">- Please!
- Hey, marry me!</font>

165
00:10:32,420 --> 00:10:34,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's a man whore.</font>

166
00:10:37,260 --> 00:10:39,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Y-You sold me out!</font>

167
00:10:43,510 --> 00:10:44,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">- The worst.
- Scum.</font>

168
00:10:44,810 --> 00:10:45,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Trash.</font>

169
00:10:46,020 --> 00:10:47,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">- Too bad.
- What a letdown.</font>

170
00:10:58,900 --> 00:11:03,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I feel horrible. I'm sorry.
I don't know what came over me earlier.</font>

171
00:11:03,530 --> 00:11:05,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's nothing.</font>

172
00:11:05,160 --> 00:11:07,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They were just pigeons anyway.</font>

173
00:11:08,370 --> 00:11:10,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What is going on with me?</font>

174
00:11:10,920 --> 00:11:11,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Elizabeth!</font>

175
00:11:12,080 --> 00:11:14,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Next time I won't forgive you!</font>

176
00:11:14,500 --> 00:11:15,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Got it?!</font>

177
00:11:22,970 --> 00:11:26,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Make sure to keep her safe
next time, okay?</font>

178
00:11:49,710 --> 00:11:51,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What are you going to do now?</font>

179
00:11:51,830 --> 00:11:56,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Run, Keisuke.</font>

180
00:11:59,800 --> 00:12:01,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">- After him!
- No, wait.</font>

181
00:12:01,720 --> 00:12:04,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Even if we let him go, we have a hostage.</font>

182
00:12:04,850 --> 00:12:06,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He'll be back
sooner or later.</font>

183
00:12:12,940 --> 00:12:16,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll come back for you, Father!</font>

184
00:12:16,400 --> 00:12:18,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please hold on!</font>

185
00:12:23,860 --> 00:12:26,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What are you doing, Elizabeth?</font>

186
00:12:26,530 --> 00:12:28,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm making lunch.</font>

187
00:12:28,620 --> 00:12:29,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey!</font>

188
00:12:29,540 --> 00:12:32,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've seen this fish before!</font>

189
00:12:32,460 --> 00:12:35,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's the same one
that was on Pop's back!</font>

190
00:12:36,790 --> 00:12:39,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's called a carp, Piyoko.</font>

191
00:12:40,010 --> 00:12:40,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Line caught?</font>

192
00:12:41,050 --> 00:12:42,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Absolutely not.</font>

193
00:12:43,760 --> 00:12:47,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I just sent a current through a location
in the pond where I though carp would be.</font>

194
00:12:48,060 --> 00:12:49,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Easy, right?</font>

195
00:12:49,310 --> 00:12:51,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I didn't know you could do that.</font>

196
00:12:51,180 --> 00:12:52,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Looks like fun!</font>

197
00:12:53,100 --> 00:12:54,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wanna do that too!</font>

198
00:12:55,020 --> 00:12:56,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Can I do it too?</font>

199
00:12:58,820 --> 00:13:00,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hmm...</font>

200
00:13:00,190 --> 00:13:03,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It might be a few months
too soon for you.</font>

201
00:13:05,360 --> 00:13:08,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can catch a carp too,
you know!</font>

202
00:13:09,120 --> 00:13:11,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll use this—</font>

203
00:13:15,040 --> 00:13:17,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Like I said, it's too soon for you.</font>

204
00:13:18,210 --> 00:13:21,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll overlook this for now...</font>

205
00:13:23,170 --> 00:13:25,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh! There's something just right
for her to do over there...</font>

206
00:13:26,180 --> 00:13:27,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Piyoko...</font>

207
00:13:27,180 --> 00:13:30,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Could you please pick me three
dandelion flowers for me over there?</font>

208
00:13:30,560 --> 00:13:32,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I want to add them to the food.</font>

209
00:13:32,140 --> 00:13:34,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Flowers to decorate our food, right?</font>

210
00:13:34,390 --> 00:13:36,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's easy peasy!</font>

211
00:13:37,900 --> 00:13:40,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Flowers...flowers...</font>

212
00:13:41,530 --> 00:13:43,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There are so many flowers,
aren't there?</font>

213
00:13:44,400 --> 00:13:45,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

214
00:13:46,030 --> 00:13:49,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">These flowers are small and cute,
just like me!</font>

215
00:13:49,780 --> 00:13:51,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll get these!</font>

216
00:13:52,660 --> 00:13:54,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Those are flowers too, Piyoko...
But...</font>

217
00:13:55,920 --> 00:13:59,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The dandelions that
I wanted you to get are these.</font>

218
00:14:01,380 --> 00:14:03,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I just took a side route</font>

219
00:14:03,670 --> 00:14:06,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and I was going to
get those flowers later on!</font>

220
00:14:06,760 --> 00:14:09,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you got them already,
then I guess this was all pointless!</font>

221
00:14:14,140 --> 00:14:18,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The last step is to season it
with salt and pepper, and...</font>

222
00:14:19,520 --> 00:14:20,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">...it's done!</font>

223
00:14:21,320 --> 00:14:24,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">White fish saute with a
two-tone vegetable sauce,</font>

224
00:14:24,240 --> 00:14:25,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and a dandelion garnish.</font>

225
00:14:25,820 --> 00:14:28,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yay! I love fish!</font>

226
00:14:28,860 --> 00:14:30,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is it edible?</font>

227
00:14:30,160 --> 00:14:31,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How rude!</font>

228
00:14:31,240 --> 00:14:32,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Cooking is one of my talents,
okay?!</font>

229
00:14:34,160 --> 00:14:36,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I mean, how good can it be?</font>

230
00:14:41,380 --> 00:14:43,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Delicious!!!</font>

231
00:14:43,920 --> 00:14:47,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What is this? The vegetable sauce
perfectly complements the carp,</font>

232
00:14:47,430 --> 00:14:51,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">neutralizing the fishiness
while drawing out full-bodied flavor!</font>

233
00:14:51,510 --> 00:14:52,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It tastes just like the time</font>

234
00:14:53,010 --> 00:14:55,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I ate a grasshopper
and a frog at the same time...</font>

235
00:14:55,680 --> 00:14:58,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and a revolution occured
on my tastebuds! It's better than that!</font>

236
00:15:00,150 --> 00:15:01,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm a genius!</font>

237
00:15:02,020 --> 00:15:03,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's eat!</font>

238
00:15:03,730 --> 00:15:04,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wait!</font>

239
00:15:15,240 --> 00:15:17,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I have the smallest portion!</font>

240
00:15:19,920 --> 00:15:22,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?! They're the same size!</font>

241
00:15:22,380 --> 00:15:24,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nope! This corner on
this one is missing!</font>

242
00:15:25,050 --> 00:15:26,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't be greedy!</font>

243
00:15:26,340 --> 00:15:28,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The only thing small here,
is your character!</font>

244
00:15:28,420 --> 00:15:30,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just be grateful you're
getting a portion!</font>

245
00:15:30,380 --> 00:15:32,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Give me another half,
then I'll be grateful!</font>

246
00:15:33,850 --> 00:15:35,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">- Hey! Don't mess around!
- Let me eat more!</font>

247
00:15:35,560 --> 00:15:37,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">- Absolutely not!
- Let me eat more!</font>

248
00:15:37,310 --> 00:15:39,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let me eat more!</font>

249
00:15:39,270 --> 00:15:40,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let me eat more!</font>

250
00:15:40,980 --> 00:15:42,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let me eat more!</font>

251
00:15:42,650 --> 00:15:46,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, Mister, I'm not hungry,
so you can have mine!</font>

252
00:15:46,780 --> 00:15:47,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, thank you !!</font>

253
00:15:49,950 --> 00:15:51,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

254
00:15:51,240 --> 00:15:53,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You'd eat a child's portion?!</font>

255
00:15:53,620 --> 00:15:54,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You scum!</font>

256
00:15:54,700 --> 00:15:57,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So delicious!!</font>

257
00:15:57,870 --> 00:15:59,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Spit it back out right now!</font>

258
00:15:59,540 --> 00:16:00,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No can do!</font>

259
00:16:04,540 --> 00:16:06,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So? Any more info
on the White Demon?</font>

260
00:16:06,750 --> 00:16:07,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No.</font>

261
00:16:08,300 --> 00:16:10,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's nothing
since his last appearance.</font>

262
00:16:10,930 --> 00:16:13,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I haven't found any new leads since.</font>

263
00:16:14,430 --> 00:16:18,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All we can do right now is head
to where he was last sighted.</font>

264
00:16:18,390 --> 00:16:21,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We might find a clue there.</font>

265
00:16:22,060 --> 00:16:25,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We still have
at least 250 kilometers to go...</font>

266
00:16:25,480 --> 00:16:26,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

267
00:16:26,820 --> 00:16:28,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Come to think of it...
Where's Piyoko?</font>

268
00:16:32,280 --> 00:16:34,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?! Only one bug?</font>

269
00:16:34,370 --> 00:16:36,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We told you to catch ten,
didn't we?</font>

270
00:16:36,280 --> 00:16:37,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You messin' with us, huh?!</font>

271
00:16:37,990 --> 00:16:40,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">C-Catching ten is impossible!</font>

272
00:16:40,370 --> 00:16:41,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please forgive me!</font>

273
00:16:41,830 --> 00:16:44,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is there some reason
why you can't follow my orders?</font>

274
00:16:44,580 --> 00:16:48,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You know what happens now,
don't you?!</font>

275
00:16:49,380 --> 00:16:50,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Die!</font>

276
00:16:51,050 --> 00:16:52,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hold it!</font>

277
00:16:58,350 --> 00:16:59,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you hurt?</font>

278
00:16:59,810 --> 00:17:00,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">N-No!</font>

279
00:17:00,890 --> 00:17:02,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Who the hell are you?!</font>

280
00:17:02,440 --> 00:17:03,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hmph!</font>

281
00:17:03,350 --> 00:17:04,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Me, you say?</font>

282
00:17:06,810 --> 00:17:09,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm "Dutiful Piyoko"!</font>

283
00:17:07,110 --> 00:17:13,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}DUTY</font>

284
00:17:09,440 --> 00:17:13,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I live by Pops' credo and
I never let evil off the hook!</font>

285
00:17:14,700 --> 00:17:16,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My entrance is spot on!</font>

286
00:17:17,280 --> 00:17:20,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So this little chick wants to fight us?</font>

287
00:17:20,830 --> 00:17:24,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Fine. I'm happy to oblige.</font>

288
00:17:24,620 --> 00:17:26,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We're gonna kill you!</font>

289
00:17:42,930 --> 00:17:47,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Phew! Think twice before
doing anything bad ever again, got it?</font>

290
00:17:48,810 --> 00:17:52,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Damn it. I'm not done here!</font>

291
00:17:54,280 --> 00:17:56,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do it! I dare you!</font>

292
00:17:56,740 --> 00:17:58,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kiss my butt!</font>

293
00:18:01,540 --> 00:18:03,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Unforgiveable!</font>

294
00:18:03,660 --> 00:18:07,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're not getting away with this!</font>

295
00:18:10,960 --> 00:18:11,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

296
00:18:22,470 --> 00:18:25,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Demon alert issued.</font>

297
00:18:26,140 --> 00:18:28,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">- Demon alert issued.
- Get back here!</font>

298
00:18:29,060 --> 00:18:30,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Danger.</font>

299
00:18:30,270 --> 00:18:32,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">- Evacuate the area immediately.
- Get back here, you brat!</font>

300
00:18:33,150 --> 00:18:35,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Stop right now, you brat!</font>

301
00:18:35,990 --> 00:18:39,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm not stopping!</font>

302
00:18:39,160 --> 00:18:40,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Come back here!</font>

303
00:19:10,810 --> 00:19:12,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">P-Pops!</font>

304
00:19:30,580 --> 00:19:34,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're a billion years too green
to face off against me!</font>

305
00:19:34,710 --> 00:19:35,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?!</font>

306
00:19:53,400 --> 00:19:54,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Was that—?</font>

307
00:19:56,110 --> 00:19:57,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you hurt, Piyoko?</font>

308
00:20:04,700 --> 00:20:06,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wait... Piyoko?</font>

309
00:20:16,710 --> 00:20:20,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why am I so weak?</font>

310
00:20:20,720 --> 00:20:26,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why can't I be useful
for the Mister, like Elizabeth?</font>

311
00:20:26,760 --> 00:20:29,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I always need to be saved.</font>

312
00:20:29,930 --> 00:20:33,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, Mister, I'm not hungry
so you can have mine!</font>

313
00:20:39,780 --> 00:20:41,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I know full well..</font>

314
00:20:41,280 --> 00:20:44,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">...that that's all I can offer.</font>

315
00:20:44,660 --> 00:20:48,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I know I'm useless and
nothing more than dead weight.</font>

316
00:20:49,660 --> 00:20:54,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But I don't want to be that!
I don't want to be a burden to him!</font>

317
00:20:58,630 --> 00:20:59,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Maybe...</font>

318
00:21:01,800 --> 00:21:06,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">...my time with him is coming to an end.</font>

319
00:21:11,230 --> 00:21:12,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is her stomach upset?</font>

320
00:21:12,940 --> 00:21:15,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I think she might be
depressed about something.</font>

321
00:21:16,310 --> 00:21:17,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Keiji...</font>

322
00:21:18,440 --> 00:21:20,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've been a little concerned
about something.</font>

323
00:21:21,320 --> 00:21:24,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We've been with Piyoko
for about a month now...</font>

324
00:21:24,200 --> 00:21:28,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}DUTY</font>

325
00:21:24,780 --> 00:21:28,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But she hasn't grown at all.</font>

326
00:21:28,950 --> 00:21:31,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Any way you look at it,
isn't that strange?</font>

327
00:21:32,290 --> 00:21:34,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So, you noticed too.</font>

328
00:21:41,130 --> 00:21:42,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Who the hell are you?</font>

329
00:21:43,050 --> 00:21:44,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I...</font>

330
00:21:44,760 --> 00:21:46,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I finally found you...</font>

331
00:21:47,220 --> 00:21:48,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Big...</font>

332
00:21:48,850 --> 00:21:49,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">... Brother.</font>

333
00:21:50,890 --> 00:21:52,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A-Are you all right?!</font>

334
00:21:54,230 --> 00:21:55,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">W-What did he...</font>

335
00:21:56,690 --> 00:21:58,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">...just say?!</font>

336
00:23:40,000 --> 00:23:44,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's finally time for the
Goshikidori Family to make our entrance.</font>

337
00:23:44,380 --> 00:23:48,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But Keisuke, this town feels
dangerous.</font>

338
00:23:48,510 --> 00:23:51,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Next time:
Not All Feathers Hold a Song.</font>

339
00:23:51,510 --> 00:23:54,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, I've located a lady!</font>

340
00:23:54,890 --> 00:23:59,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}FAN ART CONTEST AWARDS</font>

